t sure, but he thought this was another default mes\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 
sage in the valley that interested his Agency so much. The uncertainty, the gap in his knowledge, bothered him, however, and he made a note to check on this. Did they burn the stalks?
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0      Presently, sensing no watchers around him, Depeaux sat up with his \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 back against the oak\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
