t put down an uneasy feeling that he was watched. The \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 l\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 owering sun was picking up his trail with a shadow line, too. No helping that; the crushed grass represented a track, and it could be traced.

\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0      He had driven through the town of Fosterville at 3:00 A.M., curious about the sleeping community where, so he\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 
 was told, they generally refused to answer questions about the farm. There had been a new motel on the outskirts and Tymiena had suggested they spend a night there before reconnoitering the farm, but Depeaux was playing a hunch on this case. What if ther
