\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0      Depeaux returned to the gap in the grass and had another look into the valley. There had been a massacre of Indians here in the late 1860\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s \hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0 \hich\f0 
