\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0      There was the Outsider female to be sure of first. He judged that she could be revived for questioning. That would\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 
 please Nils. It pleased Saldo now. He began to sense a greater interest in this female. She was possessor of fascinating odors. There were alien Outsider soaps and perfumes over faint, but familiar, musks. He bent close to sniff at her, the first Outside
