\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 t\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 hat she be kept for breeding. It would be interesting to breed with her.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      A female in his band snarled at him then, a wordless sound of deep menace. Another said, \'93\loch\f0 This Outsider female isn\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t a breeder! What are you doing with her?\'94
