\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      The one who had snarled at him found her voice, \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Many of these wild ones are fertile.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      The other said, \'93\loch\f0 She killed five of us. She\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s fit only for the vats.\'94
