\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 c\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 h a waste. Her flesh would be good for nothing but the vats.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      He arose, restored his nightmask to its position over his nose, and said, \'93\loch\f0 Bind her and carry her to the Hive. See that she does not escape. Two of you go to her vehicle. Bring it in for sal
