\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0      A worker came down the beaten-grass path from the Hive, waving to attract Saldo\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s attention. There was still no sign of dawnlight, but it had turned colder as it often did here just b
