roval that Saldo was doing all the necessary things. Saldo had the instincts of a good protector.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Tell me what has happened and what you have done,\'94\loch\f0  Hellstrom said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Have you had no report from the ones I sent to you?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 They reported, but I\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0  would prefer that the leader of this search troop give me his own assessment. Sometimes, workers miss important things.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0      Saldo nodded. Yes, that was wise. He told Hellstrom of the discovery of the Outsider female, the shooting, left out no detail, ev\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 en to the wound on his own jaw.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Should your wound be treated?\'94\loch\f0  Hellstrom asked, peering at it. What devilish bad luck if they lost Saldo, too!
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 It\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s a minor wound,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Saldo said. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 No worse than a small burn.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 Take care of it as soon as you r\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0 eturn.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0      Saldo heard concern for him in Hellstrom\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s voice, was warmed by it.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 I heard Old Harvey choose you as his second-in-command,\'94\loch\f0  Hellstrom said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 I was his choice.\'94\loch\f0  Saldo spoke with calm confidence.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 Have any of the others displaye\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0 d evidence of resenting this?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Nothing serious.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0      Hellstrom liked that answer. It said Saldo was aware of incipient challenges but felt able to deal with them. He no doubt could deal with them, too. Saldo carried himself well. He possessed a sure
\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0  sense of rightness. There was about him that unspoken air of dominance. It must be tempered, though.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Did you enjoy it when you were chosen by Old Harvey?\'94\loch\f0  Hellstrom asked, keeping his voice flat.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0      Saldo swallowed. Had he done something wrong? Th\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 ere\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
d been a prying coldness about that question. Had he put the Hive in peril? But Hellstrom was smiling faintly, a thin movement of his mouth beneath the nightmask.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 I enjoyed it,\'94\loch\f0  Saldo admitted, but there was uncertainty in his tone.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0      Hellstro\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 m heard that self-questioning quality in the younger man\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s voice, and he nodded. Uncertainty bred caution. One could go from liking authority into a gambler
\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s stance:  overconfident. Hellstrom explained this now in a quiet voice that carried only between \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 t\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 hem. When he\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 
d finished, Hellstrom said, \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Tell me everything you have ordered here.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0      Saldo thought for a moment, then took up his account where he had left off. He spoke with noticeable hesitation, questing in his own mind for possible errors, for nee\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 ded corrections.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Hellstrom interrupted to ask, \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Who was first to see the Outsider female?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Harvey,\'94\loch\f0  Saldo said, recalling the motion of the old man\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s hand, the upthrust pointing finger to denote his discovery. A trickle of perspiration ran down 
\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 Saldo\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s cheek. He wiped at it irritatedly and the action burned his wound.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 What orders did he give then?\'94\loch\f0  Hellstrom asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 He had told us earlier that we were to circle her when we found her. We carried that out without orders.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 What did \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Harvey do then?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 He had no chance to do anything. The female turned on her light and immediately began shooting.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0      Hellstrom looked down at the ground between them, glanced around. Several nearby workers had left their tasks out of curiosity and \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0 had moved closer to listen. \'93\loch\f0 Why aren
\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t you workers doing as your leader ordered?\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Hellstrom demanded. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Your leader gave you specific instructions. Carry them out.\'94\loch\f0  He turned back to Saldo.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 They are tired,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Saldo said, defending his workers. \'93\loch\f0 I will \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0 make a personal inspection of their work before leaving.\'94

\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0      This one is a jewel, Hellstrom thought. He defends his people, but not too much. And he takes personal responsibility without hesitation.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Exactly where were you when she began shooting?\'94\loch\f0  \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 Hellstrom asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 I was at the other end of the sweep from Harvey. When we closed the loop, I found myself beside him.\'94
