zed mind which could reproduce most conversations from memory. He was hampered this time, however, by the necessity of screening every scrap through a self-protective analysis. Unconsciously, he lost his fake British accent as he proceeded. Peruge found t
\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 h\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 is amusing.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Presently, Peruge interrupted, \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 So she went looking for Carlos.\'94
