d read the reports and \hich\f0 \endash \'94\loch\f0  He shrugged.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Agents do die in the line of duty,\'94\loch\f0  Merrivale argued.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 Of course, \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0 of course,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Peruge said. \'93\loch\f0 It\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s perfectly ordinary.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0      Merrivale scowled, obviously thinking the facts were being twisted to damn him.
