Damnable business! So the little clerk had finally bought it. His legendary caution had failed him at last. Unless that caution had somehow pulled him through. Carlos might still be alive. Somehow, Peruge did not give much weight to that possibility. The 
\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 f\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0 irst pawn had been taken, then the second and the third. Now, it was time for a more powerful piece. He said, \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Did Carlos and Tymiena quarrel about this job?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Perhaps.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 What does that mean?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 They were always snapping at each other. Who no\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0 ticed after a while?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 And we don\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t have them here to ask,\'94\loch\f0  Peruge mused.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 I don\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t need reminders of that.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Do you recall what Carlos said when you last saw him?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 Certainly; he told me he\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 d report within forty-eight hours of his arriv\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0 al on the scene.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 That long? Did they have radio?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 There was one in the van they picked up in Portland.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 And no reports from them after that?\'94
