\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 He wanted time to get set up on the scene, to reconnoiter the area, choose his observation site.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 Yes, but \hich\f0 \endash \'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 That was not an unreasonable delay.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 But Carlos was always so cautious.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0  \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0     \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 This speaks of caution,\'94\loch\f0  Merrivale objected.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 Why didn\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t you order him to make more frequent periodic calls?\'94
