\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 We should\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 ve understood that about Outsiders,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Hellstrom said. \'93\loch\f0 
They are not very good humans, the wild ones. They commonly waste their workers this way. The on\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
es who intruded here were expendable stock. I know now that it would have been far wiser for us to confuse them and send them away with a believable story.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 It was a mistake to kill them?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 A mistake to make it necessary to kill them.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0      Sald\hich\af0\dbch\af23\loch\f0 \hich\f0 o nodded his understanding of the fine distinction. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 We made a mistake,\'94\loch\f0  he said.
